
# Test Task 

This is a test task for Builg company in Full Stack Developer position. 

written by Arzoyan Ruben.




## Tech Stack

**Client:** Next JS V14, TailwindCSS, (custom css)

**Server:** Node v20, PostgreSQL, Strapi CMS


## Run Locally

Clone the project

```bash
  git clone https://github.com/Arzoyan/user-list-nextjs.git
```

We have 2 projects here. We need to install both. task-api for backend and task-front for frontend.
the firs instal backend using this following steps

Go to the task-api directory

```bash
  cd task-api
```

Install dependencies

```bash
  npm install
```

Start the server

```bash
  npm run develop
```
Now install frontend using this following steps,
Open new terminal. Go to the task-front directory

```bash
  cd task-front
```

Install dependencies

```bash
  npm install
```

Start the server

```bash
  npm run dev
```

